BAKKER v. NETHERLANDS-AMERICAN STEAM NAV. CO. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. November 14, 1916.) No. 34. In Error to the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. Edwin G. Davis, of New York City, for plaintiff in error. M. L. Fearey, of New Yqrk City, for defendant in error.

Before COXE, WARD, and HOUGH, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed.
